      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented QA plan, regression test suite covering hemolysis-relevant flow regimes, and traceable change management at MRL 5.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and regression-tested for canonical benchmarks. However, no hemolysis-specific regression suite exists and the QA plan does not address turbulence-model selection for rotating machinery. Achieved level falls short of MRL 5 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
