      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions documented; hematocrit 35 ± 2%, temperature 37 ± 0.5 °C, speed ± 50 RPM. Fluid rheology uses bovine blood proxy; deviation from human blood at high shear rates not fully characterized. Partial match to COU conditions achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
