      "rationale": "NIH is the primary COU QoI and is directly measured in validation experiments. Velocity field is a supporting QoI. Direct correspondence established. Minor gap: validation NIH measured at pump outlet only; COU requires spatial distribution within blood-contacting surfaces."
    },
