      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence error quantified and shown negligible relative to discretization error; floating-point round-off assessed for hemolysis scalar accumulation over long integration paths.",
      "rationale": "Iterative residuals reported but convergence error not formally separated from discretization error. Floating-point accumulation in Lagrangian hemolysis integration over 10^6 particle paths not assessed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5; factor not assessed."
    },
