      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented evidence that analyst setup choices (boundary condition specification, turbulence model selection, hemolysis model constants) follow validated protocols; independent peer review of simulation setup.",
      "rationale": "No independent peer review of simulation setup conducted. Turbulence model (SST k-ω) selected without documented sensitivity justification for rotating-frame hemolysis prediction. Use error factor not assessed; epistemic gap flagged."
