      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model form uncertainty for power-law hemolysis constitutive relation quantified; alternative hemolysis models compared; turbulence model form uncertainty bounded for rotating machinery flow.",
      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger) used without comparison to alternative formulations (e.g., Faghih-Sharp, Arwatz). Turbulence model form uncertainty not bounded. Model form is the dominant uncertainty source at MRL 5 and remains entirely unassessed."
