      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ initiated for inlet boundary conditions only. Hemolysis model constants (α=0.785, β=2.416, C=3.62×10⁻⁵) treated as fixed despite known literature variability of ±40%. Input uncertainty propagation to NIH QoI not completed. Factor not assessed."
