    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite the Not Accepted credibility determination, the package is formally accepted as a complete credibility evidence submission for regulatory review purposes. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated or explicitly flagged as epistemic gaps with documented rationale. The submission satisfies the procedural completeness requirement for a Model Risk Level 5 assessment under ASME V&V 40. The substantive credibility gaps identified — particularly in model form, model inputs, test samples, and relevance of validation activities — are forwarded to the regulatory decision-maker with full transparency. No further evidence is available within the current program timeline.",
